 * target    : NUCLEO-L4A6ZG
 ******************************************************************************
 * wiring    :
 * LED Output Pins
 * PA0 - CN10-29 - LED Pin 1 
 * PA1 - CN10-11 - LED Pin 2
 * PA2 - CN10-13 - LED Pin 3
 * PA3 - CN9-1   - LED Pin 4
 ******************************************************************************
